OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FDR Congo soldiers get death
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fsentence for cowardice     
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, A court in the east of the Democratic  
OL,6, Republic of Congo has sentenced seven  
OL,7, soldiers to death for cowardice in the 
OL,8, face of the enemy and murder.          
OL,10,FThey were found to have fled advancing 
OL,11,FM23 rebels, retreating through the town
OL,12,Fof Sake where they caused the death of 
OL,13,Ftwo people by recklessly discharging   
OL,14,Ftheir arms.                            
OL,16,FTheir lawyers plan to appeal.          
OL,18,FLast November, three other soldiers    
OL,19,Fwere convicted of cowardice and        
OL,20,Fsentenced to death.                    
